text_raw:
2. The 3rd day of August 2021 is appointed as the day on which Parts 1 and 
2 and sections 30, 32 and 33 of the Counterfeiting Act 2021 (No. 16 of 2021) 
shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

29 July, 2021. 

HEATHER HUMPHREYS, 

Minister for Justice. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 3rd August, 2021.
